  // resource types exist in the committed estate yet (scope:"greenfield" per-
  // service manifests, except lambda which stays scope:"estate"), so
  // cross-op references within this lane (a Cognito app client's user pool,
  // an Amplify branch's app, an SES identity's configuration set) carry a
  // synthetic-but-address-shaped value matching the sibling create op's own
  // key, exactly like the compute/database lanes above. References to types
  // the estate already runs for real (lambda functions) reuse a committed
